column5: Beautiful day out of Jordan calm seas and lots o sunshine. Picked up one in 49 fow on a walleye minnow silver/yellow/red combo off the board. Not big but a nice eater (first salmon for me in a long time so I am happy)
Way to go grog,things are starting to pick-up there as well,its been hammer time around the welland canal area with some big kings caught....cheers
Nice fish. At least you got something for you effort, enjoy the fish.
